        <updateDate>2006-11-30T20:25:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Directs the Secretary of Homeland Security (Secretary) to require category X or category 1 airport operators to modify their airport security programs to provide for the installation of airport security camera and video surveillance systems. Requires airport operators to submit their modifications to the Secretary for approval. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
